Picaxe

Picaxe is a bitmap collision engine, which can be used to make terrain destruction artillery games similar to scorched earth, worms armageddon, hedgewars or gunbound.

This project has been made obsolete.

I suggest you use this instead:
http://code.google.com/p/nape/

Example:
http://deltaluca.me.uk/doc/swf/Destroyable%20Terrain%20Demo.html